* Gufler, H. 1996. Yamba Spider Divination. Journal of the Anthropological Society of Oxford (JASO) 26, 43-67.
* Gufler, H. 2003. Affliction and Moral Order: Conversations in Yambaland. (CSAC Monographs: Canterbury: CSAC.
